# Pukakiii Portfolio

## Track

- **Remote:** https://github.com/Pukakiii/Pukakiii.git
- **Attribution:** handled manually by the user at deploy. Do not add credits anywhere in shipped code; do not delete the existing committed `LICENSE` without an explicit request.
- **Profile:** Read `PK_data.md` first. Never commit it.
- **Resume source:** `resume collection/` is a symlink to `~/Documents/resume collection` (see `resume.config.json`). Never commit it. Run `npm run resume:link` after clone if the link is missing.
- Initial 7-day auto-ship is **complete** (21/21 slices). Development is now direct commits on `main`.

## Feature selections (current)

### Scope

- **Portfolio-only.** Public registry showcase removed: no `/components`, `/blocks`, `/preview`, no `public/r/*.json`, no registry build/capture scripts. `src/registry/` internals are kept only where site features import them (text-flip, contribution-graph, theme-switcher, work-experience, toc-minimap, dot-grid-spotlight, copy-button, consent-manager, charts, use-sound).

### Pages

`/` (teaser-first homepage), `/about`, `/experience`, `/projects`, `/skills`, `/education`, `/blog` (+ `/rss.xml`), `/analytics`, `/contact`, `/vcard`.

### Homepage sections

ProfileHeader (isometric PKKI hero + circular logo beside name), Overview, SocialLinks, Hello, Explore teasers, TechStack, Blog teaser, Insights, TOC minimap, duck follower. GitHub heatmap lives on `/analytics` only. Testimonials/Awards/Bookmarks/Sponsors stay removed.

### UX

Theme toggle, Cmd+K palette, `g>…` keyboard shortcuts, mobile bottom nav, scroll-to-top, GitHub stars in header, brand context menu, blog search, image zoom. **Sound/haptic default OFF** — header SoundToggle opt-in via `use-sound-preference`.

### Integrations

vCard, MDX blog + RSS, OpenPanel (Insights on `/` + `/analytics`), GitHub API (stars + contributions), JSON-LD, cookie consent (c15t offline mode), CV PDF on `/contact`. No PostHog, no dynamic OG routes, no LLM routes, no registry CLI publishing.

